title: Healing Circles
cleaned_text: All groups are free Spiritual Solutions Talking Circle Wednesdays 6:30 p.m. - 8:00 p.m. Open to all adults seeking a connection with community, healing, and recovery through prayer, traditional blessings, and ceremonies. For more information about this wellness circle, contact [Willow Rouillard](mailto:wrouillard@sdihc.onmicrosoft.com) or call 619-234-2158 Ext 170.
